Hello Josh  This isn't too hard   The D+ terminal on the gen goes to the D+ 
on the reg. ausing a heavy red wire, The Df terminal on the gen goes to the Df 
terminal on the reg. using a small blue wire, then the brown ground wire goes 
to the screw on the gen to the body of the reg. below thw D+ terminal  thats 
all that comes off the gen. to the reg. Later and have fun  Mark Dearing  Salem 
Import Service  Salem Va
